      "description": "Looking for a dependable vehicle that gets the job done without breaking the bank? This car is in fair condition and offers a practical, honest ride for its next owner! While it shows some expected wear from its journeys, it remains a functional and spirited choice for anyone seeking value and reliability on a budget. It's ready to hit the road and serve you well!",
