    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive dual-VANOS rebuild. The rod bearings have been replaced with treated shells for long-term reliability. Performance is sharpened by a refreshed suspension featuring Bilstein dampers and poly-bushes, ensuring the chassis remains communicative. While the finish reflects its status as a well-loved driver's car, the drivetrain remains potent with crisp throttle response from the individual throttle bodies. Recent fluid analysis confirms excellent engine health.",
